stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> idea : /prd-start &lt;idea&gt;
    idea --> draft : capture rough notes into PRD spec
    draft --> in_review : /prd-review (Codex runs review + adversarial)
    in_review --> draft : /prd-revise (findings need work)
    in_review --> approved : /prd-approve (all findings triaged)
    approved --> split : /prd-split (decomposes into issue specs)
    split --> archived : /prd-archive (only when every accepted finding has receipt)
    archived --> [*]

    note right of in_review
        Codex review writes findings to JSONL.
        Every finding gets a disposition:
        - must-fix
        - optional
        - deferred
        - rejected-with-reason
        No finding may stay unset.
    end note

    note right of draft
        Scope enforcement: while in
        draft, edits are restricted
        to the PRD file itself.
        Concurrent PRD/issue blocked.
    end note
